  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Virtual Foundry</strong> is an educational simulation game created as a graduation thesis. The app is intended as a teaching tool presenting selected elements of the foundry process. Enter the interactive world of a virtual foundry and independently perform activities related to foundry process.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4430750/extras/70b81b1278905830e8161610ecfa06ff.avif?t=1774019016\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter the <strong>Virtual Foundry</strong> and prepare for work. Familiarize yourself with health and safety regulations, put on your protective gear, and learn what working in a modern foundry is like. During your shift, you will gain knowledge in preparing various sand molds and assembling metal molds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4430750/extras/e3e4a25e3f66bfbdf17fe4c3e0dbcfd1.avif?t=1774019016\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn how to use an induction furnace. Set its position, turn on the heating, add the appropriate amount of metal, and wait for the metal to melt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4430750/extras/d02f1f025c9adcd4a8fb1df7a0c2fcf0.avif?t=1774019016\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make castings in various forms and ensure their highest quality.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Virtual Foundry</strong> is an educational simulation game created as a graduation thesis. The app is intended as a teaching tool presenting selected elements of the foundry process. Enter the interactive world of a virtual foundry and independently perform activities related to foundry process.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4430750/extras/70b81b1278905830e8161610ecfa06ff.avif?t=1774019016\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter the <strong>Virtual Foundry</strong> and prepare for work. Familiarize yourself with health and safety regulations, put on your protective gear, and learn what working in a modern foundry is like. During your shift, you will gain knowledge in preparing various sand molds and assembling metal molds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4430750/extras/e3e4a25e3f66bfbdf17fe4c3e0dbcfd1.avif?t=1774019016\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn how to use an induction furnace. Set its position, turn on the heating, add the appropriate amount of metal, and wait for the metal to melt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4430750/extras/d02f1f025c9adcd4a8fb1df7a0c2fcf0.avif?t=1774019016\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make castings in various forms and ensure their highest quality.</p>",
